                        <additions>
                            <list>
                                <item xml:id="e1">
                                    <desc>Mentioned in the supplications throughout are <persName ref=""/>, 
                                    his daughters <persName ref=""/>, <persName ref=""/>, and 
                                    his son <persName ref=""/> (e.g. <locus target="#69vb #108va"/>). The names of the daughters have been added later
                                        between the lines.
                                        All names have often been erased. The colophon indicates that a woman sponsored the production of the manuscript
                                    and donated it to a church. Her name has been erased, but it might be speculated that she was a family member
                                    of the persons mentioned thoughout - possibly <persName ref=""/>, as the last two characters of her name
                                    seem to have been <foreign xml:lang="gez">ግል</foreign>.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
